frus:attachment.p:
Noting with approval the efforts of the UN
negotiators to achieve a just and honorable armistice to bring an end to the
fighting in Korea in accordance with United Nations principles;

Endorses the positions which the United Nations
negotiators have taken on the issues on which agreement has been reached, as
well as on the question still in issue;

Calls upon the Chinese Communist and North Korean
authorities to avert further bloodshed by responding favorably to the
outstanding proposals of the UN negotiators;
